  "notes": "Captured against Shopify Admin 2026-04 with 49 disposable baseline PRODUCT pins and exact bounded identity/resource/pinned/window cassettes. `pin: false` unpins the temporary position-50 definition, `pin: true` then pins a second definition at position 50, constrained update pin returns `UNSUPPORTED_PINNING`, and updating another definition with pin at the 50-definition boundary returns `PINNED_LIMIT_REACHED`. Cleanup deletes all disposable definitions and restores the original pins."
